      Press release
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Northern Irish F gas users urged to prepare for change ahead of 1 January 2021
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Producers, suppliers, traders and end-users will need to take action to prepare for the end of the transition period</p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
    <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds metadata-column">
